title: The A Word - soundtrack
description:
Here's my effort at an unofficial (ie not very good) soundtrack to the BBC series "The A Word".  I don't watch much telly, but the missus watches this and I've been pleasantly surprised with some of the tunes I've overheard!

I don't claim to have every song from the programme, and there's no way I'd have any of that Will fucking Young shit.....

1. Mardy Bum by Arctic Monkeys
2. What Do I Get? by Buzzcocks
3. World Shut Your Mouth by Julian Cope
4. Don't You Want Me by The Human League
5. Another Girl, Another Planet by The Only Ones
6. Upside Down by Paloma Faith
7. If You Could Read My Mind by Gordon Lightfoot
8. A Certain Romance by Arctic Monkeys
9. Accidents Will Happen by Elvis Costello & The Attractions
10. Another Girl, Another Planet by The Only Ones
11. Ever Fallen In Love (With Someone You Shouldn't've) by Buzzcocks
12. Disco 2000 by Pulp
13. Rip It Up by Orange Juice
14. Something Changed by Pulp
15. Take Me Out by Franz Ferdinand
16. Teenage Kicks by The Undertones
17. Common People by Pulp
18. I Bet You Look Good on the Dancefloor by Arctic Monkeys
19. Reward by The Teardrop Explodes
20. Ace of Spades by Motorhead
21. Going Underground by The Jam
22. Don't You Want me Baby by The Human League
23. Secret Heart by Ron Sexsmith

Most are MP3, a couple of FLAC - I don't care, just listen to the music!

Please SEED!
